of Life, working out this last breakthrough

01:33.382 --> 01:39.232
of Self-realization.

01:39.682 --> 01:52.412
And this happening is a living happening,
a spontaneous happening, the way a seed sprouts

01:52.412 --> 02:02.293
spontaneously when it is embedded in the Mother
Earth.

02:02.293 --> 02:17.572
The problem with the human mind is such that
he thinks or it thinks that it can work out

02:17.572 --> 02:30.372
