form.

03:06.533 --> 03:19.652
But we cannot understand that whatever we
may try, we cannot lay our hands on the living

03:19.652 --> 03:24.313
process.

03:24.313 --> 03:29.663
Only after Self-realization you are entitled.

03:29.663 --> 03:35.003
You get powers to do living work.

03:35.003 --> 03:46.232
That is the sign of a person who is born again,
who is a yogi, who has had a union with the

03:46.232 --> 03:47.232
