07:17.263 --> 07:26.433
In the same way, within you lies this potential
which is to be manifested.

07:26.433 --> 07:37.173
We have been also told about the left and
right side within us.

07:37.173 --> 07:44.203
Left and right side are the only two sides
to which our attention can go, which represents

07:44.203 --> 07:47.043
our sympathetic nervous system.

07:47.043 --> 07:50.243
That is when you go into any emergency.

07:50.243 --> 07:57.363
Suppose you are rushing somewhere or running,
your sympathetic goes into action and creates

07:57.363 --> 08:03.603
the results necessary for that action.

08:03.603 --> 08:11.293
For example, you have to run; so the sympathetic
will start pumping the blood fast, will start

08:11.293 --> 08:16.273
breathing fast.

08:16.273 --> 08:23.953
But what brings it back to normal is the central
path, what we call represented in the medical

08:23.953 --> 08:28.733
terminology as parasympathetic nervous system.

08:28.733 --> 08:34.613
So in our own effort we can only go to the
left or right.

08:34.613 --> 08:42.693
