to understand.

09:31.823 --> 09:37.483
The physical problems come to us because of
our imbalances.

09:37.483 --> 09:44.043
In various ways we try to go to the left or
to the right.

09:44.043 --> 09:51.343
Now, let us see how cancer is caused because
that is the headache of today, or maybe of

09:51.343 --> 09:57.293
