pool; suddenly it opens out for you.

19:19.642 --> 19:31.662
Or maybe you open some sort of a shower and
it becomes a torrential rain -- so many choices

19:31.662 --> 19:35.452
which maddens you completely.

19:35.452 --> 19:40.613
What is there to choose about how you'll have
your scissors?

19:40.613 --> 19:46.202
As long as the scissor work, it should be
all right.

19:46.202 --> 19:51.733
It is so complicated because so much of machinery
-- they have to produce so many things, so

19:51.733 --> 19:54.932
many varieties!

19:54.932 --> 20:02.272
Right from A to Z, whether it is a dress,
whether it is a hair-do, whether it is a carpet,

20:02.272 --> 20:10.542
or it is an ordinary thing which we call as
the handle of the car.

20:10.542 --> 20:16.012
Before getting into the car better ask the
driver how it operates otherwise you'll be

20:16.012 --> 20:17.312
lumped?[locked].

20:17.312 --> 20:26.402
There is no uniformity kept about these useless
material things and so the choices are so

20:26.402 --> 20:27.402
many.

20:27.402 --> 20:32.483
