that's gone out of market.

21:12.223 --> 21:17.613
Now another thirty-two things have come!

21:17.613 --> 21:27.582
All such maddening things put you to thinking,
"What should I do?"

21:27.582 --> 21:32.873
Then we have to plan out everything in the
future.

21:32.873 --> 21:40.442
It is so much so that by temperament, people
have become futuristic.

21:40.442 --> 21:46.142
