22:00.632 --> 22:03.272
They do not know the plan of the Divine.

22:03.272 --> 22:08.863
They'll plan it out: rush, go forward, do
this, go to the airport.

22:08.863 --> 22:09.873
What has happened?

22:09.873 --> 22:13.883
The plane is delayed three hours!

22:13.883 --> 22:14.883
Why?

22:14.883 --> 22:18.623
Because their condition, holiday cancelled.

22:18.623 --> 22:22.452
They had planned the holiday a year ahead.

22:22.452 --> 22:28.182
Poor things, you see, packed everything to
go somewhere.

22:28.182 --> 22:32.493
Holiday had to be cancelled because the planes
are not moving.

22:32.493 --> 22:34.932
So they sit down on the airport.

22:34.932 --> 22:37.912
See, they're waiting for something to happen.

22:37.912 --> 22:43.892
Nothing happens; they go off.

22:43.892 --> 22:49.623
But a yogi does not plan.

22:49.623 --> 22:53.572
He knows what's going to happen.

22:53.572 --> 22:55.802
He does not bother.

22:55.802 --> 23:01.403
But supposing a yogi gets lost on the way.

23:01.403 --> 23:07.662
Then he thinks, "All right, if I am lost there
must be something here.

23:07.662 --> 23:09.282
I must see it.

23:09.282 --> 23:10.503
I am there with myself.

23:10.503 --> 23:11.932
I am not lost.

23:11.932 --> 23:14.412
So let's enjoy."

23:14.412 --> 23:18.143
After all, what are we going to miss?

23:18.143 --> 23:25.312
It is something one has to see that as we
are so much stressed and under the domination

23:25.312 --> 23:35.422
