rush, rush.

23:35.422 --> 23:40.993
Even the jobs that we do, we are supposed
to rush.

23:40.993 --> 23:50.432
You will rush as much as you like but the
problem is your mind also rushes with it and

23:50.432 --> 23:53.353
the whole personality gets involved into it.

23:53.353 --> 24:02.262
But if you have seen a wheel, the whole wheel
moves but the axis has to be steady.

24:02.262 --> 24:07.493
If the axis also starts moving, there is stress.

24:07.493 --> 24:17.632
That's exactly what happens to us that we
start moving with all the tensions that are

24:17.632 --> 24:21.093
