29:37.022 --> 29:45.353
So this poor spleen doesn't understand -- this
personality which is all the time under shock.

29:45.353 --> 29:51.392
Then you get into our car and on the road
there is a jam.

29:51.392 --> 29:52.392
Finish!

29:52.392 --> 29:56.772
You had to reach at such and such time; now
it's a jam.

29:56.772 --> 30:03.682
Now you are cursing everything, sitting down
there worrying.

30:03.682 --> 30:05.552
Suddenly you find an accident.

30:05.552 --> 30:09.713
Then you go in the office or some place where
you are working.

30:09.713 --> 30:15.082
The boss has had a quarrel with his wife;
so he comes and shouts at you -- another shock.

30:15.082 --> 30:21.503
All the time you are facing very arrogant,
horrible people.

30:21.503 --> 30:27.272
I mean, I myself am afraid to go to shops
or anything because suddenly they jump on

30:27.272 --> 30:32.993
you like a horse or sometimes like a dog.

30:32.993 --> 30:35.622
God knows how they will react on you.

30:35.622 --> 30:37.442
You get a fright.

30:37.442 --> 30:38.993
What's the matter with them?

30:38.993 --> 30:41.363
Why are they so shocking?

30:41.363 --> 30:47.402
But all of them are under stress and they
are taking it out on you.

30:47.402 --> 30:57.863
But the worst thing that happens with this
spleen going crazy is that you get blood cancer.

30:57.863 --> 31:09.392
Blood cancer is caused by hectic life and
for speedy life that we lead.

31:09.392 --> 31:13.282
Now the blood pressure comes from the kidney.

31:13.282 --> 31:18.613
And like that so many things are caused by
one simple thing â€' that we think too

31:18.613 --> 31:21.163
much.

31:21.163 --> 31:23.973
What is there to think?

31:23.973 --> 31:26.843
I just don't understand.

31:26.843 --> 31:29.622
Whatever has to happen, will happen.

31:29.622 --> 31:33.113
By thinking, nothing is going to stop.

31:33.113 --> 31:37.213
By thinking we have achieved nothing.

31:37.213 --> 31:44.072
If you read Einstein who has developed the
theory of relativity, at the very outset he

31:44.072 --> 31:52.952
says that, "I was tired and I was lying down
in my garden, playing with soap bubbles and

31:52.952 --> 32:01.103
suddenly from somewhere unknown the theory
of relativity dawned upon me."

32:01.103 --> 32:04.263
Whatever we have is there.

32:04.263 --> 32:12.492
Whatever we have to find out comes from the
unknown, but thinking about it like mad just

32:12.492 --> 32:13.492
ruins us.

32:13.492 --> 32:16.013
But if I say, "Don't think," you can't stop
thinking.

32:16.013 --> 32:21.182
I know that because we had a wonderful doctor
in Switzerland.

32:21.182 --> 32:23.603
He came and said, "Mother, do what You like.

32:23.603 --> 32:28.072
You cut my throat, You cut my head but stop
this thinking.

32:28.072 --> 32:29.632
I am going mad."

32:29.632 --> 32:35.593
So he developed a momentum of thinking, all
the time thinking, thinking, thinking.

32:35.593 --> 32:41.093
Now what happens with the kundalini, when
the kundalini rises, passes through your Agnya

32:41.093 --> 32:48.062
Chakra, you go beyond thinking.

32:48.062 --> 32:53.182
It is like one wave of thought comes up and
goes down, another wave of thought comes up

32:53.182 --> 32:55.513
and goes down.

32:55.513 --> 33:00.353
In the center there is a little space; so
one comes from the past and goes to the future,

33:00.353 --> 33:02.912
another from the future to the past.

33:02.912 --> 33:06.713
In between there is a little space, and that
is the present.

33:06.713 --> 33:12.742
So when the kundalini rises, passes through
this Agnya Chakra â€' the one that gives

33:12.742 --> 33:19.412
you thought is the ego and the superego on
both the side, as you can see clearly -- they

33:19.412 --> 33:27.812
are sucked in; your karmas are sucked in,
your ego is sucked in, your conditioning is

33:27.812 --> 33:33.513
sucked in and you stand at the present moment.

33:33.513 --> 33:38.282
Then if you want to think, if you don't want
to think, you just sit down in complete silence

33:38.282 --> 33:40.942
and enjoy yourself.

33:40.942 --> 33:43.072
You become in command.

33:43.072 --> 33:48.603
Like you are standing in the water, you are
afraid of getting drowned, but if you get

33:48.603 --> 33:51.663
into the boat you enjoy the water.

33:51.663 --> 33:57.952
But supposing you become a master swimmer,
then you can save others also from the water.

33:57.952 --> 34:05.642
This is exactly what happens when a Sahaja
yogi establishes himself well, that he can

34:05.642 --> 34:13.752
give salvation to so many and can save so
many people.

34:13.752 --> 34:16.983
This is how we are going to emancipate.

34:16.983 --> 34:23.603
Now the emotional side that we have is also
another extreme to which we bow?

34:23.603 --> 34:30.533
And with the help of certain elements, you
will be surprised: one candle can at least

34:30.533 --> 34:38.973
cure twenty-five mad people at least.

34:38.973 --> 34:40.942
It's very simple.

34:40.942 --> 34:52.402
If you enlighten this light, then what happens
that enlightened light goes inside your left

34:52.402 --> 35:02.132
side and enlightens it completely and all
the negativity disappears in your collective

35:02.132 --> 35:03.733
subconscious.

35:03.733 --> 35:11.672
And you know who all suffer from the left
side of insanity, epilepsy, schizophrenia,

35:11.672 --> 35:16.223
all this nonsense.

35:16.223 --> 35:22.903
Because you stand in the center -- you are
neither on the left nor on the right -- if

35:22.903 --> 35:26.882
you are in the center, you get rid of your
emotional problems.

35:26.882 --> 35:31.263
Now, there are spiritual problems also.

35:31.263 --> 35:39.403
Before as we have, I told you, thinking problem,
we have also physical problems like over-exertion.

35:39.403 --> 35:41.983
Now people are jogging.

35:41.983 --> 35:46.302
It's madness, I really tell you.

35:46.302 --> 35:50.862
First, I thought there is some sort of an
earthquake that the old, young, everybody

35:50.862 --> 35:51.862
running.

35:51.862 --> 35:52.862
What is happening?

35:52.862 --> 35:53.862
What's wrong?

35:53.862 --> 35:56.353
Where are you running?

35:56.353 --> 35:59.973
Because you are over-exerting yourself.

35:59.973 --> 36:03.733
What is the need to over-exert yourself?

36:03.733 --> 36:09.254
Because now a concept is that if you are muscular
-- I don't know whatever is the concept, every

36:09.254 --> 36:14.923
day changing, every day you find new, new
things -- then you become over-efficient;

36:14.923 --> 36:15.923
you become tired.

36:15.923 --> 36:16.923
It's absurd.

36:16.923 --> 36:23.943
We have seen in history, say, we have got
the greatest statesman and the person who

36:23.943 --> 36:30.923
saved us from this horrible Hitler was Churchill
and what a fat man he was.

36:30.923 --> 36:43.443
He never did jogging in his life!

36:43.443 --> 36:45.793
I mean, you must accept your body.

36:45.793 --> 36:46.793
It requires rest.

36:46.793 --> 36:53.153
For example, if I start jogging, I'll be nowhere
Myself because I need a lot of water to protect

36:53.153 --> 36:56.183
the chakras which work out the emancipation.

36:56.183 --> 37:05.113
To Me, that is much more important than becoming
some sort of a cinema actress.

37:05.113 --> 37:06.443
There are many cinema actresses.

37:06.443 --> 37:07.613
So what?

37:07.613 --> 37:09.163
What have they achieved?

37:09.163 --> 37:14.493
How many people have they emancipated?

37:14.493 --> 37:18.862
So what is your ideal in life is to be decided
first.

37:18.862 --> 37:23.793
Do you want to be all the time slave of your
body?

37:23.793 --> 37:25.783
And I don't know what you get.

37:25.783 --> 37:28.663
I mean, these days nobody looks at no one.

37:28.663 --> 37:36.552
They are fed up now and you can't make out
one from another because they go to the same

37:36.552 --> 37:38.003
hairdresser.

37:38.003 --> 37:39.623
One fashion starts.

37:39.623 --> 37:44.783
I have to think, "Is this he same person or
somebody else?"

37:44.783 --> 37:53.793
I mean, it is better to grow your beard to
look something different.

37:53.793 --> 37:58.082
I mean, there no way of making out who is
who!

37:58.082 --> 38:03.693
Everybody has the same hair dress, everybody
has the same funny dress, everybody looking

38:03.693 --> 38:04.693
the same.

38:04.693 --> 38:07.583
They have no personality.

38:07.583 --> 38:12.862
Tomorrow a wave comes that you should put
a plastic bag on your head -- everybody will

38:12.862 --> 38:17.753
be moving with a plastic head.

38:17.753 --> 38:19.593
We have to have a personality.

38:19.593 --> 38:24.403
Why should we dress up as everybody is dressing
up?

38:24.403 --> 38:26.973
Such a pressure.

38:26.973 --> 38:32.053
I know that because I have another life which
you know very well which is supposed to be

38:32.053 --> 38:36.443
the high society -- so-called.

38:36.443 --> 38:41.903
And the stupidest thing we discuss in that
society.

38:41.903 --> 38:48.803
Like they laugh at a woman if she is wearing
something that was, say, belonging to sixties.

38:48.803 --> 38:53.003
I mean, what's the harm?

38:53.003 --> 38:55.892
No, that's not modern!

38:55.892 --> 38:59.943
But what do you gain by becoming so modern
running with the fashion?

38:59.943 --> 39:01.713
What do you gain?

39:01.713 --> 39:07.332
Now the fashion in England is to make holey
pants -- you make holes.

39:07.332 --> 39:11.132
Imagine that cold, horrible cold that you
have.

39:11.132 --> 39:17.793
What is the need to make holes in your pant
to get all kinds of troubles?

39:17.793 --> 39:20.163
And then they'll have arthritis; then they'll
have this.

39:20.163 --> 39:24.263
First they had tight pants; so they developed
varicose veins.

39:24.263 --> 39:33.013
Now they are having such loose pants that
they will develop arthritis.

39:33.013 --> 39:36.283
These people are managing you.

39:36.283 --> 39:40.203
These manufacturers are befooling you.

39:40.203 --> 39:46.963
This we cannot see because we have lost our
personality.

39:46.963 --> 39:53.433
So we develop so many problems also because
we play into the hands of nonsenses.

39:53.433 --> 40:00.852
Now, say, Indian people have lived for so
many ages now so they have learnt all the

40:00.852 --> 40:02.062
lessons.

40:02.062 --> 40:08.223
If you go and tell them that you wear a holey
pant they'll say to/you, "Get lost!

40:08.223 --> 40:09.363
Sorry, sir.

40:09.363 --> 40:10.553
We know everything."

40:10.553 --> 40:18.112
Now they are painting their hair and when
they are painting their hair, people say,

40:18.112 --> 40:20.562
"Why are you painting their hair?"

40:20.562 --> 40:23.243
"Oh, that's the fashion.

40:23.243 --> 40:24.433
What's wrong?"

40:24.433 --> 40:27.203
But people become blind in that.

40:27.203 --> 40:33.153
We had three patients who became blind because
they painted their hair and some sort of a

40:33.153 --> 40:34.653
thing -- punk, punk.

40:34.653 --> 40:39.663
They were three blind punks who came to Sahaja
Yoga.

40:39.663 --> 40:47.543
Actually, you have to punch them to talk to
them.

40:47.543 --> 40:51.463
This is the society in which we live.

40:51.463 --> 40:55.043
Anybody who is sane will think I am mad.

40:55.043 --> 41:03.173
Like going to a lunatic asylum, you start
thinking, "Am I mad or they are mad?"

41:03.173 --> 41:05.423
That's how it creates a stress on us.

41:05.423 --> 41:11.102
Let us live with our own dignity.

41:11.102 --> 41:14.892
You can see Mahatma Gandhi went for his round
table conference.

41:14.892 --> 41:18.082
He wore his dhoti.

41:18.082 --> 41:25.243
He didn't wear a three-piece suit and a tail
coat -- that's another nonsense!

41:25.243 --> 41:29.773
Everybody in England has to wear a tailcoat
when they go to the Queen's party.

41:29.773 --> 41:31.892
But they can't afford.

41:31.892 --> 41:37.263
So they borrow; some are tight, some are loose.

41:37.263 --> 41:42.993
And when you see them there -- I mean, I have
been to many of them -- you can't recognize,

41:42.993 --> 41:52.112
and they look so absurd and clownish that,
poor things, you know all these big, big ambassadors

41:52.112 --> 41:56.453
have to go about with that because it is supposed
to be a formal dress.

41:56.453 --> 41:59.913
I mean, what a formal dress it is.

41:59.913 --> 42:02.622
All these things pressurize you.

42:02.622 --> 42:07.593
They make you feel, "Oh, you must wear a dress
like this."

42:07.593 --> 42:14.693
Even when you go to some guru, he says, "All
right, you all have to wear," say, "orange

42:14.693 --> 42:15.733
dress."

42:15.733 --> 42:21.543
So you are forced into it; you have to wear
the orange dress.

42:21.543 --> 42:31.513
From where are you going to manage -- getting
rid of all this nonsense of forcing you to

42:31.513 --> 42:34.042
do this and forcing you to do that.

42:34.042 --> 42:43.142
But here you are so individualistic and here
you are a down-to-earth personality,

42:43.142 --> 42:50.903
Its not that anybody says you have to do it
but you just do it because we have our own

42:50.903 --> 42:51.903
personality.

42:51.903 --> 42:55.563
Individualism means personality.

42:55.563 --> 43:05.003
And that is what when it is lost, you feel
also your guilt and your stress.

43:05.003 --> 43:13.092
That's possible that you stand on in your
own glory, in your own personality, in your

43:13.092 --> 43:16.693
own understanding of your spiritual value.

43:16.693 --> 43:25.213
So when that starts, another style of movement
comes in, like hippies.

43:25.213 --> 43:39.302
We become like a primitive person, you become
like a hippy, you go about like a hippy, you

43:39.302 --> 43:48.023
wear a funny dress, become a primitive personality
and think, "Oh, I have done very great thing."

43:48.023 --> 43:54.093
I had some hippies with Me, I told you yesterday.

43:54.093 --> 43:59.683
So I asked them, "Why do you dress up like
this?"

43:59.683 --> 44:02.953
They said, "We want this kind of culture."

44:02.953 --> 44:04.853
I said, "This is primitive."

44:04.853 --> 44:05.853
They said, "We want to be primitive."

44:05.853 --> 44:08.053
I said, "You cannot be.

44:08.053 --> 44:09.793
Your brain is modern.

44:09.793 --> 44:14.943
Just by wearing these primitive things you
cannot be.

44:14.943 --> 44:18.753
Accept it, accept yourself.

44:18.753 --> 44:38.683
And now you have your realization and it will
work out."

44:38.683 --> 44:48.154
So with all these stresses on us -- thinking
too much, futuristic personality â€' you

44:48.154 --> 44:49.802
develop the stress.

44:49.802 --> 45:01.233
Now what happens when kundalini rises, you
are beyond thought.

45:01.233 --> 45:04.053
That's called in Sanskrit as Nirvichar Samadhi
-- thoughtless awareness.

45:04.053 --> 45:12.953
You are fully aware -- on the contrary, you
are more aware â€' but you are in thoughtless

45:12.953 --> 45:13.953
awareness.

45:13.953 --> 45:19.062
Now when I see this carpet in thoughtless
awareness, I don't think.

45:19.062 --> 45:24.112
I don't think because if I have to think,
"Oh, Baba, this is my carpet.

45:24.112 --> 45:25.713
Now I have not insured it.

45:25.713 --> 45:28.673
If somebody will run away with it, then what
will happen?"

45:28.673 --> 45:30.283
I won't be able to give any speech or anything.

45:30.283 --> 45:36.233
I'll be worried about the carpet only.

45:36.233 --> 45:39.223
But when I look at this carpet, I don't think.

45:39.223 --> 45:48.903
Only the joy of the creation of this carpet
is just pouring into Me; a beautiful blissful

45:48.903 --> 45:50.533
feeling, that's all.

45:50.533 --> 45:52.973
I am not thinking.

45:52.973 --> 46:04.102
Like a very still beautiful lake which has
no ripples reflects all the beauty that is

46:04.102 --> 46:05.953
around it, fully.

46:05.953 --> 46:18.443
A complete joy is reflected in a mind which
is absolutely still, not reacting, not accepting,

46:18.443 --> 46:22.243
just seeing, witnessing.

46:22.243 --> 46:31.463
And this witness state comes into you and
you become a tranquil and a peaceful personality.

46:31.463 --> 46:39.112
Such peace that such a person, wherever he
goes, wherever he walks, a peaceful atmosphere

46:39.112 --> 46:41.852
prevails.

46:41.852 --> 46:47.723
The nature, the elements all react to such
a personality.

46:47.723 --> 46:55.903
Just talking about peace or giving prizes
of peace, you do not feel peace.

46:55.903 --> 47:01.283
I know of people who have got Nobel Prizes
of peace are horrid.

47:01.283 --> 47:07.102
They look like some mad dogs.

47:07.102 --> 47:11.403
If you have to talk to them, take the barge
pole in between.

47:11.403 --> 47:17.573
Don't know when you'll be hit with the prize
they have got.

47:17.573 --> 47:23.592
And you may have to pay very dearly for meting
such a personality who is supposed to be the

47:23.592 --> 47:32.503
foundation of peace and you find it's a fountain
of violence.

47:32.503 --> 47:42.632
This is the situation today that we are placed
in a society which artificially expresses

47:42.632 --> 50:11.403
itself.

50:11.403 --> 50:33.003
There

50:33.003 --> 01:23:53.162
is nothing genuine, nothing innate ...
